    'message': 'You\'ve gathered near a fire. Huddled together, rubbing shoulders with strangers who have all traveled from far off lands seeking shelter and purpose in the warmth of the flames. Enthralled by the flickering flames, you watch as they turn crimson, then emerald and then indigo. Engulfed in them, the fire within you now prances to the tempo of the flames  in the grip of euphoria you hear the rhythm of the flames. Wondering where the music comes from you open your eyes  flashy strobe lights battle the enticing dark as the composer looks right into your eyes.    Prepare to be enchanted by the current ranked #12 DjMag on the grand opening night of Antaragni’17. Let the fire within resonate to the reverberation of maverick beats of this year\'s EDM artist. Witness the flames rise sky high as KSHMR takes the stage on 26th October!    Kudos to SUNBURN Festival, Percept live and Eminence Group Of Entertainment for such professionalism in the work and making this happen!  #KSHMRatAntaragni #SuitsOfEuphoria #Antaragni17',
