    'message': '‘A photograph shouldn\'t be just a picture, it should be a philosophy.’ The world seems chaotic from far.  Call it vision, imagination, or seeing  it all comes down to the same   thing: the ability to envision a final result in your mind\'s eye. Find a corner and capture the subtleties of life with your camera and send it to us at Fmc@antaragni.in before 23nd October. For more information visit: https://antaragni.in/competitions/photography/aperture #SuitsOfEuphoria #Antaragni17',
